high_descs: Go to the brown table.
Pick the knife up off of the table.
Slice the lettuce with the knife.
Take the knife to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Walk over to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and take it back out.
Walk back to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the table with cabbage
Pick up the butter knife from the table
Slice up the front cabbage on the table
Take the knife and go to the sink on the right
Place the knife into the sink
Turn around and go back to the table
Pick up a cabbage slice from the table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Chill the cabbage slice in the fridge and take it out
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the cabbage slice into the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cabbage slice in the sink

high_descs: Go straight, turn to your right, then go straight and face the brown table.
Pick up the knife that's on the table.
Cut the lettuce that's on the table with the knife.
Bring the knife with you to the right, move so that you're between the table and the sink and then face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back to the table where you cut the lettuce.
Pick up a piece of the lettuce from the table.
Turn around and bring the lettuce over to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge on the second shelf from the top, close the fridge and cool the lettuce, then take it out again.
Bring the lettuce with you and turn left, then head to the same spot you dropped the knife in the sink and face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.
